# O-Route Core

Read `AGENTS.md` for full context before non-trivial changes.

## Stack

React 18 + TypeScript (strict) + Vike SSR + Konva + Immutable.js + Firebase RTDB/Storage.

## Code style

- Function components only: `function Foo()` with `export { Foo }`
- Named exports only (except Vike `+config.h.ts` default export)
- Props: `type Props = { ... }` in the same file
- UI: MUI + `Overlay` / `ToggleButton` on canvas screens

## Change workflow

- Small branches; one concern per branch
- After changes: `npm run format` then `npm run build`
- UI / canvas / online changes: also run `npm run test:e2e` (or `npm run verify`)
- Do not merge to `master` without user approval

## Avoid

- Mutating Immutable `Record` instances in place
- Loosening Firebase security rules
- Renaming `"follwer"` without backward compatibility
- Casual edits to `OnlineCanvas.tsx` useEffect dependency arrays
- Over-abstracting for this ~1,600-line codebase
